<br>
However, you might ask this question on EQTraders.com's forums.  They have some math majors that have attempted to reverse engineer alot of tha math involved in tradeskills.<br>
<br>
I've only ever heard that were tradeskills are concerned that More is more.<br>
<br>
As an aside.  There is usually another skill (aside from int/wisdom) that also affects skillups.  For tailoring it's Dexterity.  But I've heard two different things from people.  One that it's the best of int/wis/dex (for tailoring) that determines skillup chances.  The other is that the highest os int/wis determines with an additional bonus for having a high dex (for tailoring).  I honestly don't know which is true, but I was leaning in the direction of the former.<br>
<br>
